liquibase.ext.logging.log4j2

Class Log4j2Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • liquibase.logging.core.AbstractLogger
      • liquibase.ext.logging.log4j2.Log4j2Logger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    liquibase.logging.Logger, liquibase.servicelocator.PrioritizedService

    public class Log4j2Logger
extends liquibase.logging.core.AbstractLogger
    Logs Liquibase messages to Log4j 2.x.

    This class must be in the liquibase package in order for the Liquibase plugin discovery mechanism to work.
